{"parentUuid":"ea360fcd-e1b8-4200-b1a9-8a854c5b05f0","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"97ed883d-d33c-45cd-9f31-4358d93ee749","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01K4EFhTrEFPqtdSE3J2oSjn","type":"tool_result","content":"     3→## User-Facing Features\n     4→\n     5→- **Config flow: lock reset in options flow** — Extend the lock reset step\n     6→  (clear/adopt unmanaged codes) to the options flow when new locks are added.\n     7→  Adopt should merge into existing slot config (preserve names, settings) rather\n     8→  than creating fresh entries."}]},"uuid":"db7fcbfb-bb67-41fb-8387-d075208547d8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T23:11:32.261Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager/TODO.md","content":"## User-Facing Features\n\n- **Config flow: lock reset in options flow** — Extend the lock reset step\n  (clear/adopt unmanaged codes) to the options flow when new locks are added.\n  Adopt should merge into existing slot config (preserve names, settings) rather\n  than creating fresh entries.","numLines":6,"startLine":3,"totalLines":77}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"ea360fcd-e1b8-4200-b1a9-8a854c5b05f0","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"feat/lock-reset-step","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
{"parentUuid":"db7fcbfb-bb67-41fb-8387-d075208547d8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012PhknuvmtHGVjHt9dUT4yn","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Tbfw79iDoXCtUM2AswWGd2","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager/TODO.md","old_string":"- **Config flow: lock reset in options flow** — Extend the lock reset step\n  (clear/adopt unmanaged codes) to the options flow when new locks are added.\n  Adopt should merge into existing slot config (preserve names, settings) rather\n  than creating fresh entries.","new_string":"- **Config flow: lock reset in options flow** — Extend the lock reset step\n  (clear/adopt unmanaged codes) to the options flow when new locks are added.\n  Adopt should merge into existing slot config (preserve names, settings) rather\n  than creating fresh entries. Key considerations: (1) compute \"unmanaged\" against\n  the *new* slot config being submitted, not the current stored config, so removing\n  a slot doesn't immediately offer to clear it; (2) existing managed slots on\n  write-only locks (Matter) show as UNKNOWN — filter these out using the new config\n  rather than offering to reset them; (3) if re-setting managed PINs for safety\n  after lock reset, note this to the user."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":507,"cache_read_input_tokens":394437,"output_tokens":354,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":507,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZjaPu5Vo4S5XS3iEZC64","type":"assistant","uuid":"4241e2ab-4022-470e-a0bf-4add19f6643a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T23:11:40.483Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/proj